div.p: The WÃ¼rth Online Shop is an electronic catalog and ordering system for our customers that is accessible via the Internet. The online shop gives you access to more than 28,000 products, product details, approvals and data sheets. In addition, this platform offers the possibility of efficient ordering through the use of scanners. Archives and shopping baskets can also be generated, budgets set up, cost centres managed and approval processes carried out. can be defined.

ul.li: Simple article search, also via combinations of search criteria
Quick search and display of catalogue pages, product information, safety data sheets and your current, individual prices
Simple ordering by adding the desired items to the shopping cart and tracking
Installation and management of persons with rights allocation
Order service around the clock, every day of the week
Orders are immediately forwarded to our logistics department for delivery
Use and management of desired cost centers
Purchase on account, direct debit, Paypal, credit card
Services such as ISI!!, MSDS and more!

div.p: Logistics and delivery as you need it! When ordering, you can decide whether you want the goods conveniently shipped home, to the company or to the construction site directly, or if you want to pick up the goods immediately via Click and Collect at the nearest branch. All our deliveries are shipped via 24 hour service. This means, if you place your order by 16:00 the previous day, you can expect your goods on the next working day. We offer delivery tracking online by clicking on "My Wurth" and then clicking "Orders". We also offer subscription orders, to ensure a simple and cost effective alternative. Simply subscribe to WÃ¼rth products, receive regular deliveries and reduce warehousing costs.

ul.li: Standard delivery with shipment tracking
Click & Collect â order online, pick up at the branch office
Regularly supplied with subscription orders

div.p: With the function "My office" you can create individual user accounts with different rights, Budgets and Cost Centers. If several users are using the online shop, individual functionalities are useful and also allow the administrator to keep track of orders and expenses.

ul.li: User administration with rights and role concept
Invoice and delivery note reprint
Cost center management and order value limits
Budgeting and approval workflow

div.p: Would you like our shop for professional functions such as customer-specific price frames, order templates, individual customer material numbers or for inventory? No problem! Because our online shop can do more! We are not only distinguished as the best B2B online shop, but also keep our promise and deliver free additional services.

ul.li: Customised price frames
Order templates at the customer or user level
Deposition of customer material numbers
Inventory function
Offer management

div.p: With electronic procurement you can optimize and profit from your procurement processes. and thus from the more efficient and faster procurement of your products. Whether small parts or cost-intensive A-items, the internal time and cost expenditure is always the same. Especially with C-parts, the internal process costs exceed the actual value of the goods many times over. From the order confirmation to the acceptance of the goods and inspection of the delivery up to the comparison of the invoice, everything must be recorded and processed in the accounting system. In a manual process, this means this takes a lot of time - and time is money!
div.span: Our solutions for your process optimization:

ul.li: Order files in various formats such as UGL, UGS, Datanorm or Opentrans
Electronic invoice data formats
E-Procurement functions per punchout with e.g. OCI, IDS, Ariba, cXML or ComNorm
We also can be found on E-Commerce Market Places such as SAP Ariba, Meplato, Mercateo and more!

div.p: Get in touch to see if we can provide an E-Commerce solution for you via customer.services@wurth.co.uk

ul.li: Administration of personal offers
Contact details of the contact person in the field service and the nearest branch office
Guided tutorials on functionalities
Chat or direct contact by phone
